      <p class="newsletter-description">
        Get the latest updates on solar panel recycling, industry news, and sustainability insights 
        delivered straight to your inbox. Join our community of environmental leaders.
      </p>
      <div class="newsletter-features">
        <div class="feature-item">
          <svg class="feature-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
            <path d="M13.854 3.646a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-7 7a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-3.5-3.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708L6.5 10.293l6.646-6.647a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0z" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Monthly industry insights</span>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-item">
          <svg class="feature-icon" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none">
            <path d="M13.854 3.646a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-7 7a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-3.5-3.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708L6.5 10.293l6.646-6.647a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0z" fill="currentColor"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Grant opportunities</span>
        </div>
